DATA LICENSE

The datafiles in data/ folder are derived from:
  • SNCF Open Data (https://data.sncf.com)
  • Public domain railway information

These datasets are provided under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Synthetic delay data was generated for research purposes using realistic 
distributions based on the AQST 2016 report "Causes des retards TER".

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

ATTRIBUTION

This project uses data from:
  • SNCF - Gares de Voyageurs Dataset
  • SNCF - Formes des Lignes du RFN Dataset  
  • AQST 2016 - Causes of Train Delays Report
  • SNCF 2023 - Annual Railway Balance Sheet

